data.description: You won't want to miss the opportunity to see this beautiful La Vista home and all it has to offer! Updated kitchen with newer appliances and lvp flooring lead seamlessly into the living area and back patio. New carpet throughout the lower level that offers a walk out into the large fully fenced in backyard lines with lilac bushes. Easy access to the attached garage and expansive driveway. Primary bedroom has a recently updated en suite. Guest bathroom is also newly updated! New roof and tons of potential to come in and make this home your own! Close to the new City Centre, restaurants, park and more!
